34
00:03:51.351 --> 00:03:53.351
His impression, sort of.

35
00:03:53.351 --> 00:03:54.951
His face, maybe?

36
00:03:54.951 --> 00:03:56.251
Come to think of it,

37
00:03:56.251 --> 00:03:59.351
there were rumors going around that Hado had plastic surgery.

38
00:03:59.351 --> 00:04:03.951
But that was back when Hado graduated from high school, I think?

39
00:04:03.951 --> 00:04:07.251
Like I told you before, that's all baloney.

40
00:04:07.251 --> 00:04:09.551
Because back then, both he and I had no money

41
00:04:09.551 --> 00:04:13.551
