44
00:04:20.551 --> 00:04:23.651
and marry another woman.

45
00:04:23.651 --> 00:04:26.351
If I remember correctly, he got married 16 years ago.

46
00:04:26.351 --> 00:04:30.551
And the song, "ASACA" that was supposed to be released this time

47
00:04:30.551 --> 00:04:31.951
