57
00:04:58.251 --> 00:05:01.051
that he would be releasing the new song "ASACA".

58
00:05:01.051 --> 00:05:04.651
I just know there's got to be something behind this.

59
00:05:04.651 --> 00:05:06.751
Is that true?

60
00:05:06.751 --> 00:05:12.951
No. He joined out record company 17 years ago.

61
00:05:12.951 --> 00:05:16.251
I told him jokingly that the real reason I helped him debut

62
00:05:16.251 --> 00:05:23.551
was because I fell in love at first sight with Ms. Enjo.

63
00:05:23.551 --> 00:05:26.551
He said if that's true, he was going to resign.

64
00:05:26.551 --> 00:05:27.851
I see.

65
00:05:27.851 --> 00:05:30.551
But that doesn't sound enoug to be a motive

66
00:05:30.551 --> 00:05:32.251
