67
00:05:32.251 --> 00:05:35.351
I guess I'll get already then.

68
00:05:35.351 --> 00:05:36.451
Wait!

69
00:05:36.451 --> 00:05:38.751
This is an impossible crime

70
00:05:38.751 --> 00:05:41.551
