Hey.

86
00:06:44.551 --> 00:06:48.351
That guy's been glaring this way for some time, do you know why?

87
00:06:48.351 --> 00:06:49.351
No.

88
00:06:49.351 --> 00:06:50.951
Before anything else,

89
00:06:50.951 --> 00:06:53.051
