91
00:06:56.651 --> 00:06:57.751
I know.

92
00:06:57.751 --> 00:06:59.751
Hey! Let me go!

93
00:06:59.751 --> 00:07:03.651
I've got to go back quickly and write an article about this case!

94
00:07:03.651 --> 00:07:07.251
Before that, let me confirm the contents of your bag.

95
00:07:07.251 --> 00:07:08.451
You sure are persistent.

96
00:07:08.451 --> 00:07:10.651
Let me go, I said!

97
00:07:15.651 --> 00:07:16.951
Ouch...

98
00:07:18.351 --> 00:07:20.151
The evidence!

99
00:07:20.151 --> 00:07:22.251
I'll help you pick it up.

100
00:07:22.251 --> 00:07:24.051
Thank you.

101
