Looking at the pictures that were inside the camera in your bag,

104
00:07:45.351 --> 00:07:48.451
you were secretly taking pictures of Mr. Hado who went into the hall,

105
00:07:48.451 --> 00:07:52.451
but he found you and almost took your camera away from you.

106
00:07:52.451 --> 00:07:54.451
Is that what happened?

107
00:07:54.451 --> 00:07:55.551
Yeah.

108
00:07:55.551 --> 00:07:57.751
What did he say back then?

109
00:07:57.751 --> 00:08:00.251
He just told me not to take pictures without permission.

110
00:08:00.251 --> 00:08:03.051
And besides that, Inspector,

111
00:08:03.051 --> 00:08:07.951
a back band member who was supposed to perform with Mr. Hado

112
00:08:07.951 --> 00:08:10.651
in tomorrow's live was just picked up by the narcs.

113
00:08:10.651 --> 00:08:11.751
What?

114
00:08:11.751 --> 00:08:14.951
He was arrested red-handed for possession of illegal drugs.

115
00:08:14.951 --> 00:08:18.051
Wait, forensics officer.

116
00:08:18.051 --> 00:08:19.351
What is it, sonny?

117
