119
00:08:23.551 --> 00:08:27.451
It seems that Azusa dropped only one side.

120
00:08:27.451 --> 00:08:29.851
Only one side...

121
00:08:29.851 --> 00:08:31.451
Dropped?

122
00:08:39.451 --> 00:08:42.451
No, nothing like that was found on stage.

123
00:08:42.451 --> 00:08:44.251
Then, was anything missing?

124
00:08:44.251 --> 00:08:46.751
Like wire or work gloves.

125
00:08:46.751 --> 00:08:51.151
Yeah. It seems that those two things were missing from the tool box

126
00:08:51.151 --> 00:08:53.451
that the staff put on the sleeve of the stage.

127
00:08:53.451 --> 00:08:56.251
Then, did the staff also bring the folding pipe chair

128
00:08:56.251 --> 00:08:59.151
that was beside the tool box and put it there?

129
00:08:59.151 --> 00:09:02.651
It seems to have been way inside, but...

130
00:09:02.651 --> 00:09:05.351
Hey, they said to leave the equipment as is

131
00:09:05.351 --> 00:09:07.251
because the live is canceled.

132
00:09:07.251 --> 00:09:08.551
